{"tid":1689932,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2020 年 2 月前的台灣戰線 （真春袋）","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T06:43:04.000Z","uid":23194,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c390bdce8ec9559a53e5417e480ab184595f2ef","tid":1689932,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"今日香港，明日台灣<br />\n<br />\n請各位香港手足去跟各自的台灣親戚朋友講講香港情況<br />\n同台灣朋友講講中共的本質<br />\n依賴中共的代價<br />\n好讓佢地明年一月大選時作出最好選擇<br />\n讓甴近平中華統一夢繼續發落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，亦可以去台灣page 度多留言<br />\n做個香港五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce0938772bfea524e396bede76996e8368d05ff","tid":1689932,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:27:22.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"5ce0a742275e484ace160393afe83ee113913de2","tid":1689932,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:27:39.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ec8884ab08503c8678d880b98a39a2e2980e5d22","tid":1689932,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"f10272534a61814c9608a6bfbb2c4efe48f1632a","tid":1689932,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a16fc8db9e12d2082161850ede963a6344327206","tid":1689932,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:28:45.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"644fee3d27e16429727d8e4373db6a4f2c1184eb","tid":1689932,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:28:55.000Z","